      • addToScore

        public void addToScore(double yVelocity)
        When player reaches the center of the screen, he doesn't move any higher, but the platforms move lower the distance that the player should've moved up. This distance is also added to the score and this is how score is calculated
        Parameters:
        yVelocity - is the yVelocity added to the score
